monday that the association would announce a revamped heartguide 
program this summer focusing on education with added emphasis 
on legislative and regulatory actions for clearer food labeling 
weisfeldt said the heart association was encouraged that the fda 
plans to overhaul the governments labeling program 
ms liebman was skeptical the fda has actually said that it 
plans to improve food labels but that could take another decade or 
two she said 
