and posing for pictures with him 
hu like zhao was stripped of all party posts he escaped 
official criticism however and has been allowed to attend a few 
public functions 
zhao still a party member and parliamentary deputy has not 
been seen since he went to tiananmen square on may 19 for a tearful 
meeting with students on hunger strike 
