<TEXT>
us customs inspectors at san 
juans international airport arrested a man from colombia after 
finding a pound of cocaine surgically implanted in his thighs 
officials said tuesday 
in more than 20 years with the us customs service this is 
the most bizarre form of drugsmuggling i have ever encountered or 
heard about said mamie e pollack the agencys district 
