arent happy with the representation of women in our news pages 
bylines or supervisory positions frankly no newspaper in the 
country should be 
but she added while my fellow editors and i can make changes 
in our staffs our bylines our commitment to pluralistic coverage 
we cant change the gender of the male public figures in this 
country 
