denied blacks a voice in decisionmaking 
wisconsins socalled vanna white veto has allowed gov 
tommy g thompson to rewrite legislation by striking words and even 
letters punctuation and numerals 
foes of the veto power nicknamed for the letterflipping 
hostess of the television game show wheel of fortune said it 
gives legislative power to the executive branch violating the 
