confirmed peter hollenbach public affairs officer for treasurys 
bureau of public debt 
the actual level of public debt subject to statutory limit at 
the end of the day monday was 3023 trillion thats just 9959 
billion under the statutory limit of 3123 trillion the national 
debt stood at 2989 trillion last friday 
