schwammberger in argentina he said two law officials and an 
attorney will accompany schwammberger on the trip to west germany 
scheduled may 3 
schwammberger will be handed over to justice officials from west 
germanys badenwuerrttemberg state which has jurisdiction in the 
case engelhard said 
