passengers and gold from the california gold fields the value of 
the cargo was estimated at 16 million at the time the 
columbusamerica discovery group estimates the current value could 
reach 1 billion 
more than a ton of gold has been recovered columbusamerica 
officials estimate more than 2 tons remain on the oceans floor 
efforts to raise the rest of the treasure are on hold awaiting the 
outcome of the legal battle columbusamerica officials said 
