decline in securities underwriting and merger activity 
but shearson expanded more rapidly than any firm during the 
gogo 1980s making its current retrenchment more painful and more 
costly than any other firms 
merrill lynch amp co the nations biggest investment firm 
posted the industrys biggest quarterly loss to date only three 
months ago a fourthquarter 1989 loss of 362 million after 
charges for major cutbacks 
